    26	
    27	---
    28	
    29	## Features
    30	
    31	- **Masonry Grid Layout** -- responsive, column-balanced photo grid with infinite scroll
    32	- **Multi-Format Optimization** -- automatic AVIF, WebP, and JPEG conversion via Sharp pipeline
    33	- **Topics & Albums** -- organize photos into categories with slug aliases
    34	- **EXIF Extraction** -- camera model, lens, ISO, aperture, shutter speed, focal length, GPS
    35	- **Tagging & Search** -- full metadata search across titles, descriptions, cameras, and tags
    36	- **Sharing** -- per-photo and group share links with Base56 short keys
    37	- **Admin Dashboard** -- drag-and-drop uploads, batch editing, multi-user auth (Argon2)
    38	- **Internationalization** -- English and Korean (next-intl)
    39	- **Docker Ready** -- standalone output, single-command deployment
    40	
    41	## Configuration
    42	
    43	Site configuration lives in `apps/web/src/site-config.json`:
    44	
    45	```json
    46	{
    47	    "title": "Site Title",
    48	    "description": "Site Description",
