     1	# CLAUDE.md — AI Assistant Context for GalleryKit
     2	
     3	## Project Overview
     4	
     5	**GalleryKit** is a high-performance, self-hosted photo gallery application built with Next.js 16. It features a masonry grid layout, automatic image optimization, EXIF extraction, and multi-user admin authentication.
     6	
     7	**Demo:** https://gallery.atik.kr
     8	
     9	## Tech Stack
    10	
    11	- **Framework:** Next.js 16.2 (App Router, React 19, TypeScript 6)
    12	- **Database:** MySQL 8.0+ with Drizzle ORM
    13	- **Authentication:** Argon2 password hashing, HMAC-SHA256 session tokens
    14	- **Image Processing:** Sharp (AVIF, WebP, JPEG conversion, parallel pipeline)
    15	- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS, Radix UI, shadcn/ui (new-york style)
    16	- **i18n:** next-intl (English, Korean)
    17	- **Deployment:** Docker with standalone output
    18	
    19	## Repository Structure
    20	
    21	```
    22	gallerykit/
    23	├── apps/web/                 # Main Next.js application
    24	│   ├── src/
    25	│   │   ├── app/              # App Router pages and API routes
    26	│   │   │   ├── [locale]/     # Localized routes (en, ko)
    27	│   │   │   │   ├── admin/    # Admin dashboard (protected routes)
    28	│   │   │   │   ├── p/[id]/   # Photo viewer page
    29	│   │   │   │   ├── g/[key]/  # Shared group pages
    30	│   │   │   │   └── s/[key]/  # Shared link pages
    31	│   │   │   └── actions.ts    # Server actions (uploads, CRUD)
    32	│   │   ├── components/       # React components
    33	│   │   ├── db/               # Drizzle schema and connection
    34	│   │   ├── lib/              # Utilities (image processing, etc.)
    35	│   │   └── i18n/             # Internationalization config
    36	│   ├── messages/             # Translation files (en.json, ko.json)
    37	│   ├── public/uploads/       # Processed public image derivatives (PERSISTENT)
    38	│   ├── scripts/              # DB init, migration, seed scripts
    39	│   ├── drizzle/              # Database migrations
    40	│   ├── Dockerfile            # Multi-stage production build
    41	│   └── docker-compose.yml    # Docker deployment config
    42	├── .context/                 # Review and plan artifacts generated during OMX loops
    43	└── package.json              # Monorepo root (npm workspaces)
    44	```
    45	
    46	## Common Commands
    47	
    48	```bash
    49	# Development
    50	npm install                    # Install all dependencies
    51	npm run dev                    # Start dev server (localhost:3000)
    52	
    53	# Building
